{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":924838,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":5558355,"nickname":"iRiemanr","uptime":1434572935262},"lyricUser":{"id":924829,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":5558355,"nickname":"iRiemanr","uptime":1434572935262},"lrc":{"version":18,"lyric":"[00:57.23]I read your note, and I know just what you want to hear.\n[01:10.26]It hurts less over time, but I’m not getting stronger. I just leave pieces behind.\n[01:21.77]And I can only fall so many times before I’m broke, unrecognizable.\n[02:04.62]Now all I’ve left to give is the piece that still remains, and you bring the pieces back.\n[02:23.25]Love, it only reconstructs the pain.\n[02:32.55]As time fails to elapse, I’m finding you were everything to me.\n[02:46.06]Now my future and my past are ending tragically the same\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":4,"lyric":"[by:iRiemanr]\n[00:57.23]读你留的便签，心中明了你想要的回答\n[01:10.26]时间能治愈伤痛，并不代表我会更坚强。我只留下回忆的碎片。\n[01:21.77]等我多次落寞，物是人非之后，我只会更加堕落\n[02:04.62]我留给你的那段时光依旧历历在目被你唤醒\n[02:23.25]所谓的爱情，只会唤起伤痛\n[02:32.55]无法逃脱宿命，你是我的唯一\n[02:46.06]但结局都一样  都是悲剧"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":6,"lyric":"[56980,13170](56980,300,0)I (57280,660,0)read (57940,210,0)your (58150,630,0)note(58780,1860,0), (60640,630,0)and (61270,750,0)I (62020,2670,0)know (64690,540,0)just (65230,870,0)what (66100,450,0)you (66550,1200,0)want (67750,420,0)to (68170,1500,0)hear(69670,480,0).\n[70150,10260](70150,150,0)It (70300,540,0)hurts (70840,480,0)less (71320,480,0)over (71800,1560,0)time(73360,210,0), (73570,240,0)but (73810,240,0)I(74050,30,0)’(74080,90,0)m (74170,450,0)not (74620,570,0)getting (75190,1110,0)stronger(76300,0,0). (76300,480,0)I (76780,540,0)just (77320,360,0)leave (77680,840,0)pieces (78520,1140,0)behind(79660,750,0).\n[80410,44550](80410,330,0)And (80740,300,0)I (81040,300,0)can (81340,840,0)only (82180,960,0)fall (83140,840,0)so (83980,1260,0)many (85240,2640,0)times (87880,1050,0)before (88930,360,0)I(89290,30,0)